WEBVTT

00:13:00.013 --> 00:13:02.176
And so I think there's
a direct correlation

00:13:02.200 --> 00:13:04.046
between hard work and success in life.

00:13:04.070 --> 00:13:07.754
And the more you apply yourself,
I think the more the good things come.

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:13.103
CA: Mellody, you had the chance,
at Ariel, to implement and build

00:13:13.127 --> 00:13:17.548
the kind of diverse organization
that you've been articulating for

00:13:17.572 --> 00:13:20.430
and prove to yourself
that it actually worked,

00:13:20.454 --> 00:13:22.903
that it could deliver greater performance.

00:13:22.927 --> 00:13:25.292
MH: Well, we believe that intuitively,

00:13:25.316 --> 00:13:28.117
but we also believe it
based upon the results that we have.

00:13:28.141 --> 00:13:32.164
We are a believer in Scott Page's work,
the University of Michigan professor,